jsonSchemaExample.natural_language_description:
参数名: JSON Example | 作用: Example JSON object to use to generate the schema | 默认值: {
	"state": "California",
	"cities": ["Los Angeles", "San Francisco", "San Diego"]
}

inputSchema.natural_language_description:
参数名: Input Schema | 作用: Schema to use for the function | 提示: Use JSON Schema format (examples). $refs syntax is currently not supported. | 默认值: {
	"type": "object",
	"properties": {
		"state": {
			"type": "string"
		},
		"cities": {
			"type": "array",
			"items": {
				"type": "string"
			}
		}
	}
}

jsonSchema.natural_language_description:
参数名: JSON Schema | 作用: JSON Schema to structure and validate the output against | 默认值: {
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "state": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "cities": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    }
  }
} | (必填项)
